des:
This is an amazing application for electronic enthuse people. This app can say about some cool fact's of electronics and define some basic electronic components.

Alexa tell electronica about led 
Alexa launch electronica ---> This will launch an amazing fact about electonics
Alexa ask electronica about resistor (Ask for any basic electronic component i.e Resistor, Capacitor, led, Transistor ) -----> This will give the definition of the respective component.
